  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Types of apartments</strong></p>
<p><br />All apartments have a kitchenette with hotplates, oven, fridge/freezer, dishwasher, TV, bathroom; wc. Most have mountain or village views apart from the 2-room apt (C6) which is village view only.</p>
<p><strong>Studio Apartment (A4) 29m² - sleeps 2-4</strong> Living area with balcony and double pull-out bed plus a cabin room with bunk beds or a double/twin pull-out bed.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Studio Apartment (B4) 35m² - sleeps 2-4</strong> Living room with double pull-out bed, cabin area with double/twin beds.</p>
<p><strong>2-room Apartment (C6) 45m² - sleeps 3-6</strong> Living room with double pull-out bed, separate double bedroom and a cabin room with either bunk beds or a double pull-out bed.</p>
<p><strong>3-room Apartment (D8) 70m² - sleeps 4-8</strong> Living room with double pull-out bed, separate double bedroom and separate twin room plus a cabin room with either bunk beds or two twin beds.</p>
<p><strong>Included</strong> Bed linen and towels.</p>
<p><strong>Local Expenses</strong> Refundable deposit of €300 (studio) , €400 (apartment) or €600 (D8 apartment). Cleaning not included but this can be paid for locally from approximately €65-€100.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
